main event: Observers tracked a peculiar object moving erratically near the Nebraska Missile Site on 3 September 1965.
interesting points: The object was observed for 1 hour and 40 minutes,Initial reports indicated it was an unknown object, but it was later classified as an Astro (Natural) object,Five successive observations were made of the object which had yellowish-white, green, and white lights,Around eight young civilians and military personnel reported sighting the object, The object was described as being about 50 feet long and 15 feet wide.
witness description: Sergeants, two neighbors, eight young civilians, and military personnel
